 "data": "@startuml
title Blog System ERD with Constraints and Indexes

entity \"Users\" as Users {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 username: VARCHAR(50)
 password: VARCHAR(255)
 email: VARCHAR(100) <<Unique>>
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
 role: ENUM('USER', 'ADMIN')
 ' Unique index on email
}

entity \"Posts\" as Posts {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 user_id: INT
 title: VARCHAR(255)
 content: TEXT
 category_id: INT
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
 public_status: ENUM('PUBLIC', 'PRIVATE')
 ' Foreign Key Constraints
 ' Indexes
 ' Index on user_id and category_id
}

entity \"Categories\" as Categories {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 name: VARCHAR(100) <<Unique>>
 ' Unique index on name
}

entity \"Tags\" as Tags {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 name: VARCHAR(100) <<Unique>>
 ' Unique index on name
}

entity \"PostTags\" as PostTags {
 post_id: INT
 tag_id: INT
 ' Composite Primary Key
 ' Foreign Key Constraints
 ' Indexes
 ' Index on post_id and tag_id
}

entity \"Comments\" as Comments {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 post_id: INT
 user_id: INT
 content: TEXT
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
 ' Foreign Key Constraints
 ' Indexes
 ' Index on post_id and user_id
}

entity \"Replies\" as Replies {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 comment_id: INT
 user_id: INT
 content: TEXT
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
 ' Foreign Key Constraints
 ' Indexes
 ' Index on comment_id and user_id
}

entity \"Likes\" as Likes {
 +id: INT <<PK>>
 post_id: INT
 user_id: INT
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 ' Unique Constraint on post_id and user_id
 ' Foreign Key Constraints
 ' Indexes
 ' Index on post_id and user_id
}

' Relationships
Users --o Posts : has >
Users --o Comments : writes >
Users --o Replies : writes >
Users --o Likes : likes >
Posts --o Comments : has >
Posts --o PostTags : tagged with >
Posts --o Likes : has >
Posts --o Categories : categorized in >
Comments --o Replies : has >
PostTags --o Tags : tagged with >

@enduml",
 "format": "svg"
